{"tid":633741,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A]妖怪幻想鄉","createTime":"2018-04-18T14:38:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T15:11:23.000Z","uid":112948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9a0a0dd6add133cc80e405edb035da34d91dfd01","tid":633741,"uid":112948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T14:38:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/18/223352_886c58336135694865220143f890dfb5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F18%2F223352_886c58336135694865220143f890dfb5.jpg&h=7bfe642f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幻獸物語2公司新作 隻GAME琴日出 係玩地下城探險 打怪升LV 收集素材合裝 有拍賣所俾玩家買賣素材<br />\n<br />\n首抽流程:<br />\n一開始有3行字係俾你揀主寵<br />\n最上係黃色老鼠 中間係紅色獨眼怪 最下係藍色靈魂 揀咗好似無得轉<br />\n新手教學完有免費一抽 好似一定係廢野黎<br />\n之後去茶屋左邊紅箱拎300小判 再去神社抽11抽 最高5星 <br />\n個人覺得 付喪神/裝備 &gt; 卷物 &gt; 其他<br />\n<br />\n卷物用黎出技打怪 但好似用得一次 小心使用<br />\n綠色草用黎回血 飯團/松果用黎回飽度<br />\n<br />\n我都係啱啱開始玩 資料可能有錯 歡迎更正<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rxUOxewuaSw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrxUOxewuaSw&d=o%2FPBgnZAqpsRyg6bO2uhdP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=ed1676f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rxUOxewuaSw</a><br />\n<br />\nIOS: <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/id1000656393?l=ja&amp;mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fjp%2Fapp%2Fid1000656393%3Fl%3Dja%26mt%3D8&d=o%2FPBgnZAqpsRyg6bO2uhdP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=fcfa3f98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/id1000656393?l=ja&amp;mt=8</a><br />\nAn: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.lifemaker.Ayakashi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Djp.lifemaker.Ayakashi&d=o%2FPBgnZAqpsRyg6bO2uhdP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=e4c7aeb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.lifemaker.Ayakashi</a>"},{"pid":"2ab8f9a3935b9745246b69e771e8dbdcd293a003","tid":633741,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T14:40:55.000Z","msg":"同幻獸物語一樣畫風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"464175ac30d4755d04b5b91b8fff2047719ccc21","tid":633741,"uid":112948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ab8f9a3935b9745246b69e771e8dbdcd293a003","tid":633741,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T14:40:55.000Z","msg":"同幻獸物語一樣畫風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T14:50:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://ayakashi-g.com/info/detail/5acc64c753207\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fayakashi-g.com%2Finfo%2Fdetail%2F5acc64c753207&d=o%2FPBgnZAqpsRyg6bO2uhdP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=5368d8cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ayakashi-g.com/info/detail/5acc64c753207</a><br />\n而家有幻獸物語合作活動 可以打到濡髪童子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50b52d8bc33c96af4acb7f76eb6248ebfb32e5c0","tid":633741,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T14:51:31.000Z","msg":"課金抽野嘅pool竟然有消耗品實在係太弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我首抽11件有10件都係卷物/回復item，真係玩唔到落去<br />\n<br />\n同埋個操作好唔流暢，無論攻擊定移動手感都差，點即時戰鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74897f1103b3da0daf754a1dc01aa6cfb7515d68","tid":633741,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T14:53:05.000Z","msg":"隻game畫風同UI好高質，遊戲玩法都幾有新意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯一缺點係佢唔應該整成一隻課金抽野嘅game，哩類rogue-like地牢探索都係單機算數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829f6abb4efed603a74df65d5eba6fde340f66ae","tid":633741,"uid":112948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T15:11:23.000Z","msg":"係 抽唔到裝真係玩唔到<br />\n入場有得set倍速 但係都好難控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}